title: Ulisess Seguridad 10.6.5
description:
================
[INFO:]
================

Ulisess Seguridad 10.6.5 | 19.7 MB

Is a colletion of cracks/fixes released till date for NOD 32 Antivirus, ESET Endpoint and ESET Smart Security (x86/x64).
Works in Nod32 v2.x, ESET Endpoint 5.x & ESS-EAV 3.0/4.x/5.x/6.x/7.x

What's been added in version:

* NodLogin 10.6.5 (x86/x64)
* NOD32 Update Viewer 7.01.0 (x86/x64)

The rest of the included programs:

* TNOD User & Password Finder 1.4.2.3 (x86/x64)
* MiNODLogin 4.0.2.66 (x86/x64)
* NodLuna 14a (x86/x64)

* Box & Mara Fix 1.8 final (x86/x64)
* ESET Product Activator 2014 (x86/x64)
* ESET Product Activator 7.0 (x86/x64)
* Eset Activator 1.0.1 (x86/x64)
* ESET PureFix 2.02 (x86/x64)
* ESET NOD32 Key Finder 2013 v1.0 Premium (x86/x64)
* NodDownload 1.0 beta (x86/x64)
* Nod Key Basic 1.0 beta (x86/x64)
* NOD Generador 8.0.1 (x86/x64)
* PassNOd32 v0.0.0.0.5
* MinodServer 1.4.0.1 (x86/x64)


Operating Systems:

Windows XP/2000/Vista/Win7/Win8/Win8.1 (x86/x64)


WARNING:

* ESET can detect these utilities as a false virus.


Add into exclusions, the paths:

C:Program FilesESET*.*
C:Program FilesUlisesSoft*.*
C:Program FilesESETUlisess Seguridad*.*


Platform : Windows XP/Vista/Windows 7/Windows 8/Windows 8.1
Language : ENGLISH-SPANISH-FRENCH
